race.comment: HIGH PRECISION (2) won well two back and wasn't disgraced in stronger company at Kalgoorlie last time out. The barrier should see her in a handy position and the form out of her latest effort has already been franked. Well placed to return to winning ways. ELECTRIC BEC (7) creates plenty of interest here. She's first-up for the new stable and races over this extended trip. She was effective over 1500m when resuming at Mornington last campaign and her recent trial was very good. Can put her best foot forward. ET TU BRUTE (1) has been around the mark in recent events over further and the slight drop in trip me be what he's after. He can be closer in the run than he was last time out and the claim of ZJP comes in handy. Can be in the finish. ONLY US (3) comes through a good race at Bunbury and has claims after the claim of Cheung. LATHAMS WISH (8) is not to be discounted on recent performances.
